LAGOS  – Nigerians have been advised to seize the present time to move closer to God and shun all forms of worldliness. Pastor Sunday Sodunke of Fountain of Grace and Power Ministry gave the advice while speaking at the Church’s 10th year anniversary in Alagbole- Akute area of Ogun State. He said the church in its 10 years of existence has been preaching the same message of holiness, as he said that with all the happenings around the world, the coming of the Lord is near. ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! He urged members of the church and Christians generally in the country to beware of the spirit of the last days. “I urge everyone to beware of the spirit of the last days. Many people call themselves Christians and yet God does not know them, that is why I am appealing to them that heaven is real and hell is real, let make heaven our target. I don’t want to labour on them here on earth and at the end see them in hell. Preachers On What 2021 Has In Stock Only God Has Final Say Over Nigeria, Says Muoka “Some people left the church because they feel we are preaching holiness and righteousness not miracle, we will not tell them lies here, we will tell them the truth about the coming of the Lord, been a church member is not a license to heaven except a man be born again, that is what we preach. “Anyone that wants to go to heaven should be ready for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ. All the visions of money told by fake prophets have been the problem of these last days. A lot of people are running after mundane things of this world which is not supposed to be,” he said. Evangelist Taiwo Olutuase, who gave the sermon at the anniversary with the theme; ‘Praises To the Lord’ quoted Psalms 100 and stressed the need for all to praise God no matter the situation or condition one may be. He said thanksgiving is an act of showing gratitude to God and that that is the only thing God demands from His people. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION